==English==

===Verb===
{{en-verb|perorat|ing}}

# {{intransitive}} To [[speak]] or [[declaim]] at great length, especially in a [[pompous]] or [[grandiloquent]] manner; to [[harangue]].
# {{intransitive}} To make a [[peroration]]; to make a [[formal]] [[recapitulation]] at the end of a [[speech]].

